OL,3,CYoung family spend night in sports
OL,4,Cstadium fleeing wildfires in Greece
OL,6,FA young family from Worcestershire had
OL,7,Fto spend the night outdoors in a
OL,8,Ffootball stadium with military support
OL,9,Fafter fleeing wildfires in Greece.
OL,11,FChloe and Simon Holmes, and their two-
OL,12,Fyear-old son Oscar, from Feckenham are
OL,13,Fcurrently on holiday in Kos.
OL,15,FMr Holmes has criticised travel
OL,16,Fcompany Tui saying the family was not
OL,17,Fgiven enough information about what
OL,18,Fwas going on.
