OL,3,CYoung family spend night in sports
OL,4,Cstadium fleeing wildfires in Greece
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV Central Mr
OL,7,FHolmes said: "About 11:00 yesterday,
OL,8,Fobviously we noticed some smoke, but
OL,9,Fno one in the hotel seemed concerned.
OL,11,F"No one seemed to say anything and
OL,12,Fthat was about it. Obviously, it was
OL,13,Fgetting a bit worse and blacker.
OL,15,F"We went to dinner and about 8:30 last
OL,16,Fnight, we were back into the lobby and
OL,17,Feveryone just started just walking out
OL,18,Fand then the alarms went off. I spoke
OL,19,Fto one of the guys at the bar and he
OL,20,Fbasically said, 'You've got to go and
OL,21,Fget your passport to leave'."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
