OL,3,CYoung family spend night in sports
OL,4,Cstadium fleeing wildfires in Greece
OL,6,FThe family were then evacuated to a
OL,7,Fsports stadium where they spent most
OL,8,Fof last night outdoors.
OL,10,FMr Holmes said: "What I was concerned
OL,11,Fabout is the information I was given
OL,12,Fwas non-existent. So everyone was
OL,13,Fwhispering this and looking at Twitter
OL,14,Fand trying to find what was going on,
OL,15,Fbecause we were given no information
OL,16,Fwhatsoever.
OL,18,F"Then when we were at the stadium, the
OL,19,Fmilitary turned up with big jeeps and
OL,20,Fconvoys and tents. Everyone then
OL,21,Fstarted getting a bit more concerned.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
