OL,3,CYoung family spend night in sports
OL,4,Cstadium fleeing wildfires in Greece
OL,6,F"At 5:00 this morning, the guests were
OL,7,Fmoved indoors to a conference centre.
OL,8,FThen at 9:00 were told the coaches
OL,9,Fwere coming to take them back to the
OL,10,Fhotel."
OL,12,FBut despite now being returned to
OL,13,Ftheir hotel, Mr Holmes says
OL,14,Finformation from and organisation by
OL,15,Ftour operator TUI have been
OL,16,Finsufficient.
OL,18,FIn a statement Tui said: "The safety
OL,19,Fof our customers and colleagues is our
OL,20,Fnumber one priority.
