OL,6,F"Our teams have been working to
OL,7,Fsupport customers impacted by a
OL,8,Fwildfire in the Condamine area. Of
OL,9,Fcourse, in Greece.
OL,11,F"Coaches are now transporting guests
OL,12,Fback to their hotels, following a
OL,13,Fprecautionary evacuation order, which
OL,14,Fwas issued last night by the Greek
OL,15,Fcivil guard.
OL,17,F"We have our Tui reps on the ground
OL,18,Fsupporting customers as they return to
OL,19,Fhotels.
